{"tid":2245382,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］立法會唱票時泛民叫「五一 Save 12」口號 ，但最終建制派包攬所有主席！","createTime":"2020-10-16T07:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:12:59.000Z","uid":219007,"like":8,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"e466a4ad61d4157a16524b193dc31dabcdc8359d","tid":2245382,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/37783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F37783&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=5f11f58d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F37783&h=24c057a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/37783</a><br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】立法會18個事務委員會繼續選主席，其中、由民主派鄺俊宇主持的福利事務委員會處理多項規程問題，連提名都未完成。<br />\n<br />\n結果到散會，只得兩人獲成功提名，下次會議繼續。其他委員會，包括房屋、工商、經濟發展等，在建制派主持下均拒絕處理規程問題，只處理選舉。民主派在唱票期間當唱到5號時，會叫「五大訴求缺一不可」，唱到12號時，就叫「釋放12港人」。最終都在半小時內選出主席，均由建制派包攬。"},{"pid":"201de900ef73a1be41dcd5978a0bd9e1c611991f","tid":2245382,"uid":68689,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"Well done 要守住立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfa750f7442ed606c2a1216de8ae62d3a114151","tid":2245382,"uid":206080,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:44:55.000Z","msg":"委任今次守得好！份人工又穩了"},{"pid":"318c242a8ac1ea33c0fcc4e1b28dccf92bb1782b","tid":2245382,"uid":274722,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:46:59.000Z","msg":"最終都在半小時內選出主席，均由建制派包攬。<br />\n<br />\n議會戰線又贏，全靠泛民先拖到半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face